fltk: fltk (Fast Light Tool Kit)
fltk:
fltk: The Fast Light Tool Kit ("FLTK", pronounced "fulltick") is
fltk: a cross-platform C++ GUI toolkit for UNIX(r)/Linux(r) (X11),
fltk: Microsoft(r) Windows(r), and MacOS(r) X. FLTK provides modern GUI
fltk: functionality without the bloat and supports 3D graphics via OpenGL(r)
fltk: and its built-in GLUT emulation. It was originally developed
fltk: by Mr. Bill Spitzak and is currently maintained by a small group
fltk: of developers across the world with a central repository in the US.
fltk:
fltk: Packaged by: Widya Walesa <walecha99@gmail.com>
